        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(2 comments)\n\nThank you for fixing these. This is MUCH better.\n\nI note that you also caught two update problems. Thank you.\n\nThe switch to multi-line strings is MUCH cleaner looking.\n\nMinor comments only.\n\nPlease also write a JIRA ticket saying that the unittest code should add a mock of the database functions. Production code should NOT have code such as this:\n\nif (envPytest == 'test'):\n    # skip executing SQL in test\n    continue",
